OL,3,CMinister warns of Stormont financial
OL,4,Cblack hole
OL,6,FThe finance minister has warned of
OL,7,F'grave consequences' that Stormont
OL,8,Fdepartments have budget pressures
OL,9,Ftotalling #767m.
OL,11,FCaoimhe Archibald told the Assembly
OL,12,Fwhile the Executive expects
OL,13,F#500million in Barnett consequentials
OL,14,Ffrom the London government, there is
OL,15,F"little hope" of more money.
OL,17,FMs Archibald has also told Executive
OL,18,Fministers to take urgent action to
OL,19,Fensure they do not overspend this
OL,20,Fyear, as that will also bring a
OL,21,Ffinancial penalty for the budget.
