OL,6,F"The Executive is committed to speak
OL,7,Fwith one voice and will continues to
OL,8,Fmake the case for additional funding
OL,9,Ffor public services," she told MLAs.
OL,11,F"But the reality is with the prime
OL,12,Fminister and chancellor at pains to
OL,13,Fwarn of a painful budget coming in
OL,14,FOctober, there is little hope of
OL,15,Fadditional funding being providing
OL,16,Foutside Barnett consequentials and the
OL,17,Fbarnet formula will not deliver the
OL,18,Fadditional funding we need."
