OL,6,FOf the #767m total budget pressure,
OL,7,F90% is in health, education and
OL,8,Fjustice. More than half is needed for
OL,9,Fpublic sector pay.
OL,11,FShould Stormont fail to balance its
OL,12,Fbooks a previous offer from the
OL,13,Fgovernment to write off a #559m debt
OL,14,Fwill be rescinded.
OL,16,Fall ministers will have to play their
OL,17,Fpart by living within their budget
OL,18,Fonce this funding is provided.
OL,20,F"Not doing so would have grave
OL,21,Fconsequences for future funding.
OL,26,@|D@AOU
