OL,3,CMinister warns of Stormont financial
OL,4,Cblack hole
OL,6,F"While I, along with my Executive
OL,7,Fcolleagues, will continue to make the
OL,8,Fcase for adequate funding of our
OL,9,Fpublic services, I remain hugely
OL,10,Fconcerned that the ramifications of
OL,11,Fnot living within budget this year
OL,12,Fwould represent a potentially
OL,13,Fdisastrous outcome for the Executive
OL,14,Fand our public services.
OL,16,F"At the Executive meeting last week, I
OL,17,Foutlined to my ministerial colleagues
OL,18,Fthe need for urgent action to be taken.
OL,20,F"Collectively, we must ensure a
OL,21,Fbalanced budget is delivered.
