OL,6,F"I am currently meeting with
OL,7,Findividual ministers to discuss the
OL,8,Fbudgetary challenges and collectively,
OL,9,Fas an Executive, we will need to chart
OL,10,Fa way forward.
OL,12,F"I will continue to make the case to
OL,13,Fthe British Government that more
OL,14,Ffunding is needed for public services
OL,15,Fto support our workers, families, and
OL,16,Fbusinesses; and will be raising this
OL,17,Fat a meeting with the Chancellor later
OL,18,Fthis week.
OL,20,F"Difficult times require courageous
OL,21,Fleadership."
