OL,6,FA total of 348 MPs voted against a
OL,7,Fmotion on Tuesday, urging the
OL,8,Fgovernment to delay implementing cuts
OL,9,Ffor around 10million pensioners.JThere
OL,10,Fwere 228 MPs who voted in favour of
OL,11,Fthe motion.
OL,13,FThe winter fuel payment is an annual
OL,14,Ftax-free winter sum worth between #200
OL,15,For #300. Under the plans, the winter
OL,16,Ffuel allowance for pensioners will be
OL,17,Flimited to only those claiming pension
OL,18,Fcredit or other means-tested benefits.
