OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has justified the
OL,7,Fplans to help "secure the foundations"
OL,8,Fof the economy, but backbench MPs,
OL,9,Funion leaders, and the opposition have
OL,10,Fall called on the government to
OL,11,Freverse its decision.
OL,13,FStormont's Communities Minister Gordon
OL,14,FLyons explained the devolved
OL,15,Fadministration had no choice but to
OL,16,Ffollow Westminster in making the cut
OL,17,Fto Northern Ireland pensioners.
OL,19,FHe said he was "strongly opposed" to
OL,20,Fthe government's move.
