OL,6,F"To those who glibly say the Executive
OL,7,Fcould make a different decision, I
OL,8,Fwould ask them 'what would they cut,
OL,9,For what services would they postpone?'
OL,10,Fhe said.
OL,12,F"It is simple not credible to claim
OL,13,Fthe government have left the Executive
OL,14,Fwith any other choice."
OL,16,FMr Lyons warned the cut will have
OL,17,F"serious consequences" for the
OL,18,Fwellbeing of older people across
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland. It is thought around
OL,20,F250,000 could be affected in Northern
OL,21,FIreland.
