OL,6,FMr Lyons said: "This was a totally
OL,7,Funexpected announcement from the new
OL,8,FGovernment in Westminster.
OL,10,F"It was not mooted by the government
OL,11,Fbefore now, it was not part of their
OL,12,Fmanifesto and indeed, only a few
OL,13,Fmonths ago when the Prime Minister was
OL,14,Fleader of the opposition, he said that
OL,15,Fthe winter fuel payment should be
OL,16,Fmaintained.
