OL,6,F"Therefore, it came as a surprise to
OL,7,Fus all, that the Government would
OL,8,Fannounce the removal of this important
OL,9,Fbenefit and I can confirm that my
OL,10,Fdepartment was given no prior notice
OL,11,Fof the planned change."
OL,13,FThe Communities Minister said the
OL,14,Fprinciple of parity means that social
OL,15,Fsecurity benefits in Northern Ireland
OL,16,Fare paid at the same rates and with
OL,17,Fthe same conditions of entitlement
OL,18,Facross the UK.
