OL,6,FHe added: "The estimated additional
OL,7,Fcost to the block grant of maintaining
OL,8,Funiversal entitlement to a winter fuel
OL,9,Fpayment in Northern Ireland for winter
OL,10,F2024/25 is #44.3 million and this does
OL,11,Fnot even include any additional
OL,12,Fdelivery or staffing costs.
OL,14,F"In addition, it is estimated that an
OL,15,Fappropriate IT system to deliver
OL,16,Funiversal winter fuel payments in
